WEBVTT

00:00:02.842 --> 00:00:07.106
TAPE NUMBER TWO, INTERVIEW WITH MISTER KALMAN SHLOMOVICH.

00:00:07.887 --> 00:00:09.064
hot ir

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:12.416
gevust vos es geyt on in Daytshland

00:00:12.416 --> 00:00:13.603
mit di yidn

00:00:14.553 --> 00:00:16.454
in nayntsn akht un draysik?

00:00:17.552 --> 00:00:19.805
me ho'mir gevust nor zeyer veynik.

00:00:19.805 --> 00:00:22.268
zeyer veynik ho'mir gehat, vayl demolt

00:00:22.268 --> 00:00:23.955
hot men nisht gehat keyn,

00:00:24.298 --> 00:00:29.358
keyn yidishe tsaytung iz shoyn nisht gekumen, un s'iz nisht gevezn keyn,

00:00:30.059 --> 00:00:35.597
keyn telefonen, un keyn televizer, ale z- azolkhe zakhn zenen nisht geven, azoy vos

00:00:35.641 --> 00:00:37.238
me fleg hern,

00:00:37.238 --> 00:00:39.835
mentshn hobn dertseylt az vos se tut zikh,

00:00:39.880 --> 00:00:41.462
ober grintlekh

00:00:41.462 --> 00:00:43.641
hot men nisht gevust vos se geyt on.

00:00:43.656 --> 00:00:44.925
ikh hob gevust az

00:00:45.029 --> 00:00:48.164
der daytsh farnemt di gantse velt un er

00:00:48.179 --> 00:00:49.373
 SO...

00:00:50.109 --> 00:00:51.077
zaynen

00:00:51.077 --> 00:00:53.529
daytshishe yidn gekumen

00:00:53.771 --> 00:00:56.752
keyn Koletshave? hot ir gehat REFUGEES?

00:00:56.582 --> 00:00:59.716
NO. undz ho'mir nisht gehat keyn REFUGEES.

00:00:59.947 --> 00:01:01.185
un,

00:01:01.185 --> 00:01:03.603
ikh hob aykh fargesn fregn frier,

00:01:03.947 --> 00:01:06.641
vos far a shprakh hot ir geredt in der heym?

00:01:06.925 --> 00:01:08.044
yidish.

00:01:09.077 --> 00:01:09.665
un

00:01:09.665 --> 00:01:12.829
azoy vi ir hot gevust az es, epes geyt on, ir hot

00:01:12.829 --> 00:01:14.403
vi ir hot frier gezogt,

00:01:14.477 --> 00:01:16.986
hot ir getrakht vegn avekforn?

00:01:18.307 --> 00:01:19.381
di mishpokhe?

00:01:19.283 --> 00:01:21.328
me ho'mir nisht gehat vu tsu forn.

00:01:21.582 --> 00:01:25.776
vu vu ho'mir gekent forn, mit aza, mit di mishpokhe?

00:01:26.089 --> 00:01:31.492
s'iz nisht gevezn fun dort keyn keyn deys vu me ken aroysgeyn.

00:01:31.805 --> 00:01:34.298
undzer dorf iz gevezn

00:01:34.358 --> 00:01:36.880
arumgeleygt mit,

00:01:38.194 --> 00:01:43.029
grobekhts, ayngrobekhts far di militer ho'mir gev-, tomer di rusn kumen,

00:01:43.029 --> 00:01:44.835
hobn zey gemakht azoy azoy vos,

00:01:44.835 --> 00:01:47.343
me hot nisht gekent arumgeyn

00:01:47.343 --> 00:01:50.328
kukndik in deys, undz ho'mir gemuzt zitsn,

00:01:50.597 --> 00:01:52.402
iberhoypt a yid

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:56.179
hot nisht gek-, hot nisht gelozt forn oyf an oytobus shoyn.

00:01:56.179 --> 00:01:57.895
me hot nisht gelozt, er hot gemuzt

00:01:57.895 --> 00:02:02.313
 di letste tsayt hot men gemuzt trogn a, dem geln mogn-dovid.

00:02:02.597 --> 00:02:04.044
azoy vos,

00:02:04.179 --> 00:02:12.164
az me hot gevolt ergets araynforn me hot zikh gemuzt oystun, bahaltn far nisht keyn yid, un azoy iz men gekent durkhkhapn biz Khust,

00:02:12.253 --> 00:02:14.268
vu ikh fleg forn

00:02:14.611 --> 00:02:16.507
un brengen a bisl

00:02:16.507 --> 00:02:19.552
bronfn UNK, se zol zayn tsu farkoyfn,

00:02:19.552 --> 00:02:21.223
nor kenen lebn.

00:02:21.507 --> 00:02:25.552
vayl fun greytn tsu lebn, veyst ir, dos iz nisht a laykhte

00:02:26.089 --> 00:02:26.970
zakh.

00:02:27.647 --> 00:02:32.906
zaynt ir geblibn lebn in ayer hoyz, in di groyse hoyz, di gantse tsayt?

00:02:33.522 --> 00:02:34.731
leyder nisht.

00:02:35.671 --> 00:02:38.552
m'iz arayn, ven di ungern zenen gekumen,

00:02:38.641 --> 00:02:40.208
iz me hot gemakht di

00:02:40.238 --> 00:02:46.626
bunkers hobn zey gerufn, azelkhe vos me vu zey, vu zey flegn bahaltn zikh dos militerishe,

00:02:47.223 --> 00:02:50.746
hot men gegangen un me hot tsun undz arayngeleygt an

00:02:50.746 --> 00:02:52.283
ofitsir mit a vayb.

00:02:52.283 --> 00:02:55.582
in eyn hoy- in eyn grestn tsimer, deys.

00:02:56.373 --> 00:02:58.985
un dort hobn zey gevoynt,

00:02:59.537 --> 00:03:02.432
mit di mebl mit undzere, mit alemen,

00:03:04.104 --> 00:03:05.597
dernokh dem,

00:03:05.955 --> 00:03:08.432
zenen zey fun dort aroysgegangen,

00:03:08.865 --> 00:03:13.313
hobn zey mitgenumen ales vos iz gevezn ineveynik, undzere mebl ales hobn zey genumen.

00:03:13.850 --> 00:03:16.044
me hot gemeynt az deys iz dos argste.

00:03:16.805 --> 00:03:21.298
nokh dem hot zikh gevizn az s'iz nokh nisht, deys iz nokh nisht dos argste. undz ho'mir gehat oyf der

00:03:21.686 --> 00:03:22.318
hoyf

00:03:22.727 --> 00:03:26.818
ho'mir gehat aza zumer kokh mit an oyvn vu me hot gebakn broyt

00:03:26.818 --> 00:03:28.306
un gebakn khales,

00:03:31.193 --> 00:03:32.306
un me hot undz

00:03:32.375 --> 00:03:34.704
aroysgetribn fun undzere hoyz,

00:03:34.704 --> 00:03:36.590
me hot undz gelozt dem boydem

00:03:37.204 --> 00:03:38.284
funem hoyz,

00:03:38.647 --> 00:03:40.375
un in der zumer kokh arayn.

00:03:41.019 --> 00:03:43.967
velkhn yor, vegn velkhn yor redt ir?

00:03:44.795 --> 00:03:48.079
ikh red fun yor iz gevezn

00:03:48.079 --> 00:03:50.329
dray un fertsik, fir un fertsik.

00:03:50.334 --> 00:03:53.352
ober tsvishn nayntsn akht un draysik,

00:03:53.388 --> 00:03:54.913
un nayn-

00:03:54.924 --> 00:03:57.399
ven zaynen di ungarn arayn tsu aykh in...

00:03:57.181 --> 00:03:58.602
in akht un draysik.

00:03:58.704 --> 00:04:03.170
un ven hot, hot zikh di lage gebitn, vi azoy hot zikh di lage gebitn?

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:06.181
der lage hot zikh zeyer gikh gebitn.

00:04:06.250 --> 00:04:07.056
vi bald,

00:04:07.318 --> 00:04:12.079
ven me hot tsugenumen di di geshpar, di yidishe gevelber, ale

00:04:12.113 --> 00:04:13.897
in, vos zenen gevezn bayn undz in dorf,

00:04:14.750 --> 00:04:18.806
un me hot ale opgeshpart di tir vos, di, vegn vertshoyz,

00:04:20.193 --> 00:04:23.113
hot men gezukht parnose vos me hot gekent.

00:04:24.727 --> 00:04:26.000
un,

00:04:26.954 --> 00:04:28.181
ho'mir shoyn nisht gehat

00:04:28.181 --> 00:04:29.784
dem tvue lager,

00:04:33.784 --> 00:04:35.045
dey mentshn

00:04:36.159 --> 00:04:38.534
velkhe zey hobn undz gefirt in geto arayn,

00:04:40.465 --> 00:04:43.102
hot zikh ongerufn, ikh vel keyn mol nisht fargesn,

00:04:43.875 --> 00:04:46.681
der bak muter hot gezogt azoy,

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:49.375
"khotshik eyn mol fir ikh aykh umzist."

00:04:50.772 --> 00:04:54.318
er hot undz gefirt, velkhe me hot im gegebn parnose ale yorn.

00:04:55.079 --> 00:04:58.159
undz ho'mir genumen, undz hot er gefirt,

00:04:58.227 --> 00:05:01.965
di mame hot zikh oyfgezetst, undz ze'mir gegangen tsu fus biz Sekernitse.

00:05:02.272 --> 00:05:03.813
dos iz geven in nayntsn-

00:05:03.813 --> 00:05:04.404
ven?

00:05:04.337 --> 00:05:05.379
fir un fertsik.

00:05:04.787 --> 00:05:06.404
fir un fertsik, ober tsvishn

00:05:06.480 --> 00:05:07.720
der tsayt,

00:05:09.377 --> 00:05:10.046
v-

00:05:10.119 --> 00:05:11.885
vi azoy hot ir

00:05:12.009 --> 00:05:12.915
zikh

00:05:13.038 --> 00:05:15.749
 ayngelebt mit di ungarn?

00:05:17.136 --> 00:05:19.704
undz ho'mir nisht gehat a sakh tsu tun mit dem.

00:05:20.045 --> 00:05:22.931
undz ho'mir nisht gehat keyn, undz ho'mir gehat a,

00:05:23.238 --> 00:05:25.352
in hoyz ho'mir gehat befor,

00:05:25.534 --> 00:05:27.397
aynvoyner ho'mir genumen,

00:05:27.477 --> 00:05:29.704
iz gevezn eyner,

00:05:30.227 --> 00:05:32.670
BUSH VASILI.

00:05:32.670 --> 00:05:34.215
er iz gevezn a lerer.

00:05:34.363 --> 00:05:36.181
er iz geven zeyer a fayner mentsh.

00:05:36.375 --> 00:05:37.897
zayn a bruder,

00:05:38.113 --> 00:05:40.534
er fleg undz aroyshelfn, gebn

00:05:40.750 --> 00:05:42.693
azelkhe TOLONEN, TICKETS,

00:05:42.784 --> 00:05:48.045
undz zol'mir kenen koyfn zikh esn, tsuker, deys vos er hot ge-, er hot gearbet in a OFFICE.

00:05:48.500 --> 00:05:50.431
azoy vos,...

00:05:50.579 --> 00:05:52.727
er hot undz aroysgeholfn.

00:05:52.852 --> 00:05:57.522
bayn undz, s'iz nisht gevezn, vos me hot gegebn di TICKETS, iz dokh nisht gevezn genug tsu esn.

00:05:58.909 --> 00:06:00.295
ober,

00:06:02.409 --> 00:06:07.045
undz ze'mir nokh azoy geshtanen, az az me zol deys, ober a mentsh UNK dokh alts.

00:06:07.386 --> 00:06:10.443
di mame hot gehat a bisl a, gelt avekgeleygt far di meydlekh oyf

00:06:10.443 --> 00:06:11.318
nadn.

00:06:11.829 --> 00:06:13.045
me hot ongehoybn

00:06:14.170 --> 00:06:16.102
tsu rirn fun dem gelt.

00:06:17.943 --> 00:06:21.386
un nokh dem sof-kol-sof hot men undz avekgefirt oyf Oyshvits.

00:06:21.454 --> 00:06:23.284
un me ho'mir es in di vagonen gebrent

00:06:23.318 --> 00:06:25.534
me zol, me hot moyre gehat dos tsurikgebn.

00:06:28.419 --> 00:06:34.286
vi azoy hobn zikh oyfgefirt ayere shkheynim?

00:06:34.629 --> 00:06:35.400
un

00:06:36.941 --> 00:06:39.467
vos iz geven di batsiung tsvishn aykh?

00:06:41.329 --> 00:06:43.090
undz ho'mir gehat aza

00:06:43.147 --> 00:06:44.693
zeyer a a,

00:06:44.693 --> 00:06:45.670
galekh,

00:06:47.318 --> 00:06:52.920
vos er hot gevoynt taken a, in der tsveyter hoyz, iz er gevezn, er iz geven mit undz zeyer gut.

00:06:53.034 --> 00:06:55.375
di mame hot zikh mit im barotn

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:57.215
vos tsu tun.

00:06:58.011 --> 00:07:00.806
mayn bruder iz gehat antlofn oyf

00:07:00.806 --> 00:07:01.829
Rusland.

00:07:01.863 --> 00:07:03.295
dort iz er gevezn.

00:07:04.590 --> 00:07:09.284
hot zi zikh gezorgt az, vos vet zayn? ven er vet kumen aheym, vos, me vet aveknemen...

00:07:09.738 --> 00:07:12.288
ze'mir gegangen un me ho-, di mame hot gemakht a

00:07:12.443 --> 00:07:13.352
kontrakt,

00:07:14.795 --> 00:07:17.227
az zi farkoyft dos gantse farmegn

00:07:17.306 --> 00:07:18.772
far dem shokhn.

00:07:19.363 --> 00:07:20.715
SHOLYE MIHALYI.

00:07:22.706 --> 00:07:24.573
der shokhn iz geven der galekh?

00:07:24.340 --> 00:07:26.954
NO, der shokhn iz nisht geven, der galekh hot gezogt,

00:07:27.181 --> 00:07:29.238
"gits es far epes eynem ariber."

00:07:30.034 --> 00:07:32.113
un dos iz gevezn nokh,

00:07:32.386 --> 00:07:34.238
in eyn un fertsiker yor.

00:07:35.579 --> 00:07:37.943
vayl in eyn un fertsiker yor

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:42.568
iz gevezn, az deys me hot gegangen, me hot tsunamgenumen ale yidn

00:07:42.738 --> 00:07:44.727
fun undzere fun di ale derfer.

00:07:44.738 --> 00:07:48.204
un me hot zi geleygt in di SCHOOLn, un me hot zi gevolt avekfirn.

00:07:49.545 --> 00:07:52.045
vos iz geshen, s'iz gekumen a gezets

00:07:52.511 --> 00:07:55.488
az me zol aroyslozn velkhe zey hobn

00:07:56.761 --> 00:07:58.750
ungerishe birger-rekht.

00:07:58.875 --> 00:08:01.715
undzere shriftn zenen geven ineveynik,

00:08:02.761 --> 00:08:05.636
SO undz hot men aroysgelozt, un a sakh hot men aroysgelozt.

00:08:05.450 --> 00:08:07.166
ir zaynt geven ungarishe.

00:08:07.454 --> 00:08:11.806
deys in dem tsayt, me hot gemakht nor ungarishe, me hot nokh nisht gehat di, deys.

00:08:12.238 --> 00:08:16.522
ober di shvester mit, mit mit ire familye,

00:08:16.772 --> 00:08:18.329
mitn shvoger,

00:08:19.363 --> 00:08:23.295
in di letste minut ven s'iz shoyn gevezn dos gezets az me tor nisht firn,

00:08:23.988 --> 00:08:25.818
me hot zi aroyfgeleygt oyf a

00:08:25.852 --> 00:08:27.125
last oytos,

00:08:27.125 --> 00:08:28.625
un me hot zi avekgefirt.

00:08:30.193 --> 00:08:31.295
undz, funem,

00:08:31.465 --> 00:08:35.784
fun der, funem last oyto, hob ikh aropgenumen eyn meydele,

00:08:37.488 --> 00:08:38.624
Lanele.

00:08:39.056 --> 00:08:41.215
un zi iz bayn undz gevezn

00:08:41.215 --> 00:08:44.363
biz fir un fertsiker, biz me hot undz gefirt oyf Oyshvits.

00:08:45.852 --> 00:08:50.761
zi hot men avekgefirt, di shvester, vi me hot nokh dem gevoyr gevorn, oyf Kamenets Podolsk.

00:08:51.897 --> 00:08:53.068
dort nebekh,

00:08:53.068 --> 00:08:55.318
hot men zey aropgeleygt in a gegnt,

00:08:56.431 --> 00:08:57.897
mit di kinder,

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.750
un dort zenen zey umgekumen.

00:09:01.261 --> 00:09:03.238
keyn mol ho'mir nisht gehert mer fun zey.

00:09:03.112 --> 00:09:04.375
ven hot ir zikh

00:09:04.375 --> 00:09:05.823
bav-

00:09:06.133 --> 00:09:08.315
gevoyr gevorn vos iz geven mit zey?

00:09:08.315 --> 00:09:09.486
vos geshen mit zey?

00:09:08.375 --> 00:09:13.897
me, s'iz gekumen a sakh mentshn vos zenen zikh durkhgerisn un zenen tsurikgekumen aheym.

00:09:14.511 --> 00:09:17.238
s'iz gekumen tsun undz aheym a yid eyner,

00:09:20.022 --> 00:09:21.647
ikh gedenk nisht pinktlekh dem nomen,

00:09:21.704 --> 00:09:24.375
er iz gevezn a shmid, Strol der shmid.

00:09:25.522 --> 00:09:28.897
un der Strol hot zey gezen, er hot gezogt

00:09:29.863 --> 00:09:31.090
az

00:09:31.215 --> 00:09:35.500
zey kenen nisht geyn, zey hobn, z- zey zenen pitslekh kleyne kinder,

00:09:36.852 --> 00:09:39.227
"ir darft zey," zogt er, "nisht vartn, vayl s'iz

00:09:39.227 --> 00:09:41.090
nishto ver." er hot farshtanen az se nisht...

00:09:42.136 --> 00:09:44.852
dem Strol hot men nebekh oykhet geharget.

00:09:46.159 --> 00:09:48.363
me hot im aribergebrengt dem, me hot im getrofn,

00:09:48.636 --> 00:09:50.056
me hot gemakht a,

00:09:50.181 --> 00:09:52.579
di ungern hobn gemakht a ROZYE.

00:09:52.579 --> 00:09:54.806
zukhn tsi s'iz nishto mentshn.

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:59.181
un er iz gevezn in a shabes bayn undz oyf shaleshudes,

00:10:01.386 --> 00:10:07.545
un me hot tsunamgenumen di ale mentshn, mayn mamen hot men oykh genumen, un ale velkhe zey hobn gehat di

00:10:07.545 --> 00:10:10.840
kinder vos zenen antlofn oyf Rusland, di mume Khane,

00:10:13.340 --> 00:10:14.048
der

00:10:15.568 --> 00:10:17.146
nokh merere froyen,

00:10:17.408 --> 00:10:19.546
a rebe eyner geven, vos hot gelernt mit di kinder,

00:10:20.780 --> 00:10:24.368
hot men zey avekgefirt oyf Senever, dort iz gevezn di grenets vekhters.

00:10:26.677 --> 00:10:33.191
mayn mame hot gezogt, zey zenen gevezn groys gefar dort, ober zey hot men nisht geshlogn, nor zey hobn gehert dos geshrey fun di mener,

00:10:34.608 --> 00:10:37.523
dem Yide Hershn, nisht Yide Hersh, Motyen,

00:10:39.180 --> 00:10:42.906
hot men azoy geshlogn er iz keyn mol nisht oyfn bet aroysgegangen, er hot geshpign mit blut.

00:10:45.317 --> 00:10:46.746
un dos in dem

00:10:49.420 --> 00:10:52.734
yid vos er, der Strol mit dem andern rebe iz gevezn,

00:10:53.523 --> 00:10:56.334
hot zi gezen durkhn fentster vi azoy zey shteyen unter

00:10:56.723 --> 00:10:58.208
a deys a UNK se regnt,

00:10:58.997 --> 00:11:03.386
un zey vashn zikh funem blut, fun vi azoy, der kop iz geven blutik, fun dem...

00:11:04.231 --> 00:11:06.641
vayter ho'mir im keyn mol nisht gezen. me hot zey aroyfgefirt,

00:11:06.936 --> 00:11:11.138
me hot nokh dem getrofn oyf der grenets hobn zey geshosn un me hot zey dort ibergelozt.

00:11:11.582 --> 00:11:13.348
vu zaynt ir geven dan?

00:11:13.742 --> 00:11:15.754
ikh bin gevezn in Koletshave in der tsayt.

00:11:16.053 --> 00:11:17.634
aykh hot men nit genumen?

00:11:19.445 --> 00:11:20.924
ayer mame iz tsurikgekumen.

00:11:20.758 --> 00:11:22.363
mayn mame iz tsurikgekumen.

00:11:23.235 --> 00:11:28.154
demolts iz men gegangen, hot di mame moyre gehat, deys iz gegangen, hot men gemakht a kontrakt

00:11:28.239 --> 00:11:29.386
mit dem SHOLYEn,

00:11:29.703 --> 00:11:31.279
az me farkoyft im ales.

00:11:33.257 --> 00:11:39.485
azoy aroyf, oyf, az in tsen yor arum, oyf tsen yor, tomer keyner kert zikh nisht um,

00:11:39.745 --> 00:11:41.096
demolts gehert es tsun im.

00:11:41.561 --> 00:11:43.616
un men hot fun im nisht genumen keyn heler,

00:11:43.721 --> 00:11:46.107
er hot nisht gehat vos tsu gebn, geven an oremer

00:11:46.431 --> 00:11:47.170
shokhn.

00:11:47.691 --> 00:11:49.161
di mame hot in im gegleybt.

00:11:52.216 --> 00:11:56.199
ven mir ho'mir zikh umgekert tsurik, me hot undz, undz ze'mir shoyn in der heym gevezn,

00:11:56.452 --> 00:11:59.492
SO hot di mame dem kontrakt tsurikgenumen fun im.

00:12:01.146 --> 00:12:08.458
ober me ho'mir gemakht nokh dem a feler frish ven m'iz gegangen in fir un fertsiker yor, ven me hot genumen, zogt di mame, darf men gebn far SHOLYEn

00:12:08.564 --> 00:12:10.084
dem kontrakt.

00:12:13.469 --> 00:12:14.447
ze'mir nokh

00:12:14.848 --> 00:12:17.670
ne- gevezn in der Sekernitse, in der geto.

00:12:20.288 --> 00:12:22.463
un der SHOLYE hot shoyn gearbet

00:12:22.561 --> 00:12:24.117
iberfirn deys

00:12:24.419 --> 00:12:26.228
farmegn, dos hoyz,

00:12:26.460 --> 00:12:29.296
mitn feld, mit alemen, oyf zikh.

00:12:30.584 --> 00:12:32.885
ven ikh bin gekumen aheym fun oysn

00:12:33.118 --> 00:12:34.096
lager,

00:12:35.581 --> 00:12:37.537
hot gevoynt in undzer hoyz

00:12:37.664 --> 00:12:38.649
a

00:12:38.888 --> 00:12:39.768
BAKE.

00:12:39.768 --> 00:12:42.027
a BAKERY, vayl undz ho'mir nisht gehat shoyn

00:12:42.112 --> 00:12:43.209
in di shul,

00:12:43.308 --> 00:12:45.820
ho'mir gelozt eynem makhn a BAKERY.

00:12:46.608 --> 00:12:51.042
BAKERY hot undz gegebn, ho'mir nisht gemakht demolts keyn UNK, hot undz gegebn broyt.

00:12:51.352 --> 00:12:52.288
un

00:12:52.464 --> 00:12:56.742
s'iz geven oysgerekhnt er broykh undz gebn far tsvey meter

00:12:56.827 --> 00:13:02.387
veyts, a monheyt, dos vifl se vert, ho'mir nisht gevolt zogn in der vayl er hot nisht gevust di prayz vi azoy se vet zayn.

00:13:02.851 --> 00:13:05.413
SO er iz gevezn a ALFONS eyner,

00:13:05.483 --> 00:13:07.109
er hot undz zeyer sheyn deys.

00:13:07.165 --> 00:13:10.571
ven undz ze'mir avekgeforn iz er arayngMOVED in undzer hoyz arayn.

00:13:11.711 --> 00:13:13.457
ven ikh bin gekumen aheym,

00:13:14.751 --> 00:13:17.489
azoy hot er mir tsurikgegebn,

00:13:18.721 --> 00:13:20.571
"deys iz," zogt er, "dayn bet."

00:13:20.571 --> 00:13:23.372
de-, a dokhene mit a por kishns,

00:13:23.393 --> 00:13:27.510
deys vos vos iz geblibn in shtub, vos me hot shoyn nisht avekgenumen di alte zakhn.

00:13:27.915 --> 00:13:29.439
dos iz shoyn nokhn

00:13:29.439 --> 00:13:30.018
krig.

00:13:29.861 --> 00:13:33.330
dos iz shoyn nokh di krig, bin ikh gekumen tsurik oyf Koletshave,

00:13:33.366 --> 00:13:36.427
un zey, er iz gevezn di BAKERY hot gearbet.

00:13:37.053 --> 00:13:38.602
BAKERY hot gearbet

00:13:38.602 --> 00:13:42.092
ven s'iz gevezn akhren-shel-peysekh, ven m'iz tsurik gekumen,

00:13:42.571 --> 00:13:44.802
ikh hob aykh nisht dertseylt befor

00:13:45.196 --> 00:13:46.364
peysekh,

00:13:46.948 --> 00:13:51.818
iz gevezn a monheyt, befor peysekh, hot men al- tsunamgenumen ale mener.

00:13:52.282 --> 00:13:54.548
ale mener hot men tsuzamgenumen,

00:13:54.921 --> 00:13:58.468
un me hot gearbet mit zey. un m'iz geshlofn in a shul.

00:13:58.982 --> 00:14:00.880
ver hot zey tsuzamengenumen?

00:14:00.221 --> 00:14:01.628
dos iz gevezn,

00:14:01.755 --> 00:14:05.492
dos hot geheysn LEVENTES, heyst, velkhe zey deys.

00:14:05.626 --> 00:14:06.920
LEVENTES flegn,

00:14:06.920 --> 00:14:08.258
s'iz azelkhe

00:14:08.764 --> 00:14:10.643
arbayter vos

00:14:11.565 --> 00:14:14.957
me hot zey genumen arbetn, di yunge mentshn hot men genumen arbetn.

00:14:14.964 --> 00:14:16.006
farshteyt?

00:14:16.245 --> 00:14:18.652
, arbayts-lager?

00:14:18.400 --> 00:14:22.500
a, nisht a arbayts-lager, me hot aroysgefirt yedn tog oyf der arbet.

00:14:22.404 --> 00:14:23.485
yo, LEVENTES.

00:14:23.485 --> 00:14:25.925
ver hot dos, ver hot dos ayngefirt?

00:14:26.147 --> 00:14:31.960
dos iz gevezn ayngefirt in yede dorf, in yeder shtot. dos iz gevezn ongefirt mit dem di lerers,

00:14:32.037 --> 00:14:33.367
OKTOTORS,

00:14:33.367 --> 00:14:35.394
 ungarishe.

00:14:35.330 --> 00:14:36.826
vi, di ungarn.

00:14:36.626 --> 00:14:40.841
VITEZN, di, di HEROES fun di ungerishe fun fun

00:14:40.975 --> 00:14:43.895
ershte velt milkhome, hobn ongefirt mit dem.

00:14:43.802 --> 00:14:46.108
do- iz dos geven an armey?

00:14:46.126 --> 00:14:48.083
NO, s'iz nisht gevezn keyn armey.

00:14:48.266 --> 00:14:54.635
dos iz gevezn unter, azoy vos me hot ge- gerikhtet hot dos geheysn, vos me hot gefirt far armey, tsu lernen far armey.

00:14:54.642 --> 00:15:00.194
ober azoy di yidn hot men nisht gelernt far armey, me hot zey gegebn di LOPATES mit UNK, un zey hobn ge-,

00:15:00.222 --> 00:15:04.178
me ho'mir geCLEANED dos dorf un di di shuln mit ales vos UNK.

00:15:04.237 --> 00:15:10.340
dos, iz dos, zaynt ir geven in di ungarishe LABOR,...

00:15:08.781 --> 00:15:09.276
yo.

00:15:10.511 --> 00:15:12.440
deys iz gevezn ungarishe, yo.

00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:13.460
der ungarisher

00:15:13.467 --> 00:15:15.726
se hot gehey- a LABOR,

00:15:16.458 --> 00:15:19.681
un me hot undz aheymgelozt akhren-shel-peysekh.

00:15:19.984 --> 00:15:26.303
ven m'iz gegangen tsunamnemen, zogt er, "itster geyt aheym un port zikh oyf," vos me hot undz gefirt, fun dort, dem andern tog in di geto.

00:15:29.266 --> 00:15:30.927
ikh gedenk eyn zakh,

00:15:31.483 --> 00:15:34.734
az di mame hot ge- batsolt dort far a

00:15:34.734 --> 00:15:36.599
soldat velkher hot undz opgehit.

00:15:37.092 --> 00:15:38.591
iz er gekumen

00:15:38.746 --> 00:15:43.327
tsu di seyder nakht, er iz gezesn mit mir, ikh zol oprikhtn dem seyder far di mamen.

00:15:44.805 --> 00:15:46.311
far di kinder.

00:15:47.420 --> 00:15:49.271
ir hot gemakht a seyder?

00:15:49.309 --> 00:15:50.027
yo.

00:15:49.918 --> 00:15:50.790
ver hot...

00:15:50.555 --> 00:15:56.797
ober der soldat iz gezesn ineveynik, nokhn seyder bin ikh ts- avek mit im tsurik, in dem arayn, in shul arayn.

00:15:56.718 --> 00:15:58.698
ver iz geblibn in ayer

00:15:58.698 --> 00:16:03.631
heym ven, eyder men hot aykh genumen in geto? ver iz, ver hot gevoynt mit aykh?

00:16:03.574 --> 00:16:06.945
ale hobn gevoynt, akhuts di shvester iz nisht gevezn shoyn,

00:16:04.470 --> 00:16:05.013
ale.

00:16:07.044 --> 00:16:09.640
zi hot men avekgefirt nokh in eyn un fertsiker yor.

00:16:09.780 --> 00:16:11.310
un ayer bruder?

00:16:11.492 --> 00:16:14.975
mayn bruder iz geven antlofn oyf Unga- oyf Rusland.

00:16:13.730 --> 00:16:16.828
Rusland hot ir gezogt. iz er tsurikgekumen?

00:16:16.234 --> 00:16:19.000
er iz aropgekumen hersht in nayntsn FORTY SEVEN.

00:16:19.297 --> 00:16:21.789
er iz geblibn in Rusland di gantse tsayt.

00:16:21.787 --> 00:16:27.164
er iz geblibn, er iz geven dort in Rusland, un me hot im farshpart in tfise, un er iz gezesn dort.

00:16:26.942 --> 00:16:30.565
iz, ir zaynt geven der eyntsiker man in hoyz?

00:16:29.990 --> 00:16:31.496
ikh eyntsiker, yo.

00:16:35.058 --> 00:16:37.638
ven hot ir zikh

00:16:37.638 --> 00:16:41.229
dervust az ir darft geyn in geto?

00:16:42.337 --> 00:16:48.853
me hot undz gezogt in dem, fun dort, in dort, vi me ze'mir geven ayngeshpart, hobn zey gezogt, "geyts aheym un port zikh,

00:16:48.973 --> 00:16:55.314
, me vet geyn in geto arayn., ir vet geyn." vu nor ho'mir nisht gevust vu me gey'mir, "me firt aykh aroys."

00:16:55.275 --> 00:16:57.885
hot ir gevust az, vegn getos?

00:16:57.552 --> 00:17:01.540
NO. undz ho'mir nisht gevust, ikh hob nisht gehert dem nomen UNK, ikh hob nisht gehert far getos.

00:17:01.367 --> 00:17:07.099
hot ir gevust vos se, dan vos es geyt on in Poyln, oder mit poylishe yidn?

00:17:06.447 --> 00:17:10.719
demolts ho'mir undz nisht gevust gornisht, vayl es iz gevezn ales opge- deys, keyner hot nisht gehat keyn shum...

00:17:13.635 --> 00:17:18.979
vi azoy hot men aykh gelozt visn az az ir darft avekgeyn fun ayer hoyz?

00:17:19.333 --> 00:17:21.486
es zenen gekumen di zhandarn,

00:17:21.754 --> 00:17:25.005
un zey hobn gegebn tsu visn, "oyf in der fri zolt ir zayn greyt,

00:17:25.476 --> 00:17:27.250
es vet zayn vegn,

00:17:27.285 --> 00:17:33.293
vos ir vilt mitnemen, esn, zakh, vos ir vilt ales kent ir nemen, vos ir kent aroyfleygn oyfn vogn."

00:17:34.543 --> 00:17:36.681
vifl tsayt hot men aykh gegebn?

00:17:37.102 --> 00:17:37.996
iber nakht.

00:17:40.398 --> 00:17:42.417
vos hot ir genumen mit zikh?

00:17:44.126 --> 00:17:47.469
vos me hot genumen? s'iz gevezn akhren-shel-peysekh s'iz nisht geven keyn deys,

00:17:47.469 --> 00:17:50.213
SO der BAKE hot undz gegebn broytn,

00:17:51.825 --> 00:17:54.647
un me hot mitgenumen, iz geven shmalts

00:17:57.145 --> 00:17:59.728
un me hot mitgenumen krumpirn,

00:17:59.990 --> 00:18:01.554
vos zaynen krumpirn?

00:18:01.304 --> 00:18:02.796
deys iz kartofl.

00:18:04.837 --> 00:18:06.554
dos hot men mitgenumen.

00:18:07.476 --> 00:18:08.398
un

00:18:09.975 --> 00:18:15.548
me hot nisht tsayt gehat tsu makhn gornisht, far dem me hot gedarft geyn avek, dos iz geven a zuntik tog, s'iz gevezn

00:18:15.788 --> 00:18:17.596
khoge,

00:18:17.681 --> 00:18:23.592
keysekh iz gevezn far di, far di, dey ortodoks,

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:26.632
di, deye

00:18:27.639 --> 00:18:29.236
di ortodoksishe

00:18:30.144 --> 00:18:33.818
shu- shu- kirkhe, iz gevezn.

00:18:34.226 --> 00:18:35.267
SO,

00:18:35.345 --> 00:18:36.787
zey zenen gegangen,

00:18:37.815 --> 00:18:40.890
zey zenen gegangen, oys di kirkhe un undz hot men gefirt...

00:18:41.655 --> 00:18:43.472
hot ir genumen kleydung?

00:18:44.895 --> 00:18:46.619
me hot genumen kleydung.

00:18:46.661 --> 00:18:48.681
me hot mitgenumen di goldvarg.

00:18:49.976 --> 00:18:52.270
geklert efsher vet men kenen epes far dem,

00:18:53.304 --> 00:18:55.683
mayn mame hot gehat zeyer sheyne tsirung.

00:18:55.754 --> 00:18:58.590
mayn tate hot gehat deys, ir kent zen oyf der bild.

00:18:58.688 --> 00:19:01.813
di andere zakh ho'mir gehat vos se hot gehat sheyne

00:19:01.813 --> 00:19:03.467
zakhn, me hot mitgenumen.

00:19:03.896 --> 00:19:05.561
hot ir epes bahaltn?

00:19:06.809 --> 00:19:08.555
me hot mi- mitgenumen

00:19:08.555 --> 00:19:10.068
az me zol hobn

00:19:10.089 --> 00:19:15.071
dort ho'mir gehat dos gelt, gevust nisht, m- tsu me vet kenen, vet kenen farn gold epes koyfn.

00:19:16.212 --> 00:19:18.105
dervayl iz geblibn ales.

00:19:18.288 --> 00:19:23.889
un di dey, di daytshn hobn es, hobn dokh geheysn ales oystun zikh, di kleyder ven zey zenen gekumen oyf Oyshvits.

00:19:23.995 --> 00:19:27.521
azoy vi s'iz geblibn ales ineveynik, zey hobn undz ales tsugenumen.

00:19:27.302 --> 00:19:31.819
hot ir epes gelozt in der heym, bahaltn, oder gegebn di shkheynim?

00:19:30.302 --> 00:19:30.954
NO.

00:19:31.740 --> 00:19:34.503
NO, ikh hob nisht gegebn, undz ho'mir gegebn far shkheynim

00:19:35.100 --> 00:19:37.641
di ale skhoyres vos zenen geblibn bayn undz,

00:19:38.781 --> 00:19:42.236
vi ir veyst dokh, demolts iz gevezn a deys, s'iz geven a sh- meydlekh

00:19:42.419 --> 00:19:48.936
hot men gemakht shtafir, far yedn meydl iz geven shtafir ongeleygt, deys mit skhoyres vos farshidene...

00:19:49.541 --> 00:19:52.082
vider ho'mir gehat nokh di skhoyres fun

00:19:52.145 --> 00:19:54.341
der shvester's STORE vos s'iz gevezn.

00:19:55.157 --> 00:19:58.894
ho'mir avekgefirt, ikh aleyn hob mir gemakht, zek geneyt,

00:19:59.175 --> 00:20:00.956
befor alemen.

00:20:01.660 --> 00:20:02.919
un me hot geport,

00:20:03.166 --> 00:20:09.957
vayl me hot geshpirt az s'iz az dey vayl fun andere derfer, fun Sinever, hot men befor mit a monat shoyn avekgenumen di mentshn.

00:20:10.464 --> 00:20:14.595
azoy me hot gevust az se kumt, di shlekhte tsaytn.

00:20:14.918 --> 00:20:16.973
avekgefirt tsun eyner

00:20:18.479 --> 00:20:19.922
HAFIE,

00:20:20.478 --> 00:20:25.116
me hot zi gerufn HAFIE di amerikanke, vayl ir man iz gevezn in Amerike,

00:20:25.306 --> 00:20:27.924
un zi iz geven zeyer a shmeylike.

00:20:27.924 --> 00:20:30.211
di mame hot in ir zeyer gegleybt.

00:20:31.140 --> 00:20:32.780
un me hot ir opgefirt,

00:20:34.377 --> 00:20:39.219
dray mol iz geforn a vogn me hot gefirt di skhoyres, gefirt bahaltn bayn ir.

00:20:39.219 --> 00:20:43.054
zi hot gevoynt in a plats, in azoy in di WOOD AREA.

00:20:43.505 --> 00:20:47.235
un me hot tsun ir aropgefirt, aleyn geshlept un getrogn mit di ferd.

00:20:49.402 --> 00:20:51.872
ven ikh bin gekumen tsurik aheym,

00:20:51.972 --> 00:20:53.709
kler ikh mir,

00:20:53.709 --> 00:20:56.559
se hot mir zeyer deys, vos hob ikh tsu geyn in der velt?

00:20:56.601 --> 00:20:59.888
ikh veys undz ho'mir ibergelozt aza farmegn, me ho'mir avekgefirt tsu dem,

00:21:00.169 --> 00:21:02.865
hekhstns vel'mir zikh teyln mit ir,

00:21:02.949 --> 00:21:05.504
vos zi vet mir, vifl, vos deys,

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:07.756
vos zi vet shoyn tsurikgebn.

00:21:08.368 --> 00:21:09.860
hot zikh aroysgelozt,

00:21:09.860 --> 00:21:12.323
ikh bin gekumen in shtub arayn, un zi zogt oyf ir,

00:21:12.591 --> 00:21:13.949
zi veyst gornisht.

00:21:14.005 --> 00:21:16.299
zi hot gornisht genumen. zi hot gornisht.

00:21:17.411 --> 00:21:21.873
un ikh zog, "vos heyst, ikh dokh dir aleyn gebrengt, vi azoy kenstu zogn aza zakh, az

00:21:21.901 --> 00:21:22.668
az

00:21:23.513 --> 00:21:24.773
du host nisht?"

00:21:27.165 --> 00:21:29.375
zogt zi, "ikh zog dir az ikh hob nisht.

00:21:29.959 --> 00:21:33.204
un gey aroys fun di shtub." zi hot oyf mir gelozt di hint,

00:21:33.379 --> 00:21:38.416
a, un ikh bin gelofn avek vayl zey hobn mikh gevolt, zey zoln mikh nisht tsu esn.

00:21:39.031 --> 00:21:41.761
ober di shkheynim velkhe zey hobn gevust,

00:21:41.761 --> 00:21:44.076
hobn gezogt azoy, "undz ho'mir gezen

00:21:44.421 --> 00:21:48.883
dayne bruder's zakhn ho'mir gezen oyfn, oyf ire zin.

00:21:49.488 --> 00:21:52.592
me ho'mir gezen skhoyres, velkhe zi hot gehat.

00:21:53.162 --> 00:21:54.752
SO hob ikh gehat genumen a

00:21:54.879 --> 00:21:57.251
POLICEMAN, ze'mir avekgeforn oyf

00:22:00.432 --> 00:22:02.909
eyne a dorf eyns, vu der zun hot gevoynt,

00:22:03.655 --> 00:22:05.682
un dort hob ikh UNK gefinen

00:22:06.069 --> 00:22:10.298
epesere zakhn. ober vi azoy ho'mir es gefinen? ven undz ze'mir arayngegangen mit dem POLICE,

00:22:10.340 --> 00:22:11.544
mit dem politsyant,

00:22:11.663 --> 00:22:13.545
shoyn bay di rusishe zayt,

00:22:13.937 --> 00:22:15.091
iz zi

00:22:15.471 --> 00:22:18.750
arayngelofn, di dos vayb yenem's,

00:22:20.404 --> 00:22:21.291
un

00:22:21.446 --> 00:22:22.811
zi hot,

00:22:22.902 --> 00:22:25.577
genumen a groysn groysn koysh iz gevezn.

00:22:26.238 --> 00:22:29.975
un zi hot arayngeleygt di skhoyres vos zi hot gehat, un oyvn hot zi geleygt mit,

00:22:31.347 --> 00:22:35.436
fun bondlekh, di sholekhtser hot zi ongeleygt, un zi iz gegangen, getrogn aroys.

00:22:36.175 --> 00:22:38.758
un der POLICE hot zi geSTOPPED, "ikh vil zen vos du host dort."

00:22:38.913 --> 00:22:40.215
dort iz gevezn

00:22:41.052 --> 00:22:43.642
tsvey, dray antsiger iz gevezn.

00:22:44.557 --> 00:22:46.168
fun dem,

00:22:46.175 --> 00:22:48.026
geven epes a bisl skhoyre,

00:22:49.497 --> 00:22:51.805
s'iz gevezn froyen zakhn,

00:22:51.960 --> 00:22:54.261
deys vos ikh hob getrofn, deys hob ikh bakumen.

00:22:54.529 --> 00:22:56.387
nokh hob ikh getrofn a

00:22:56.387 --> 00:22:57.632
neymashin,

00:22:57.752 --> 00:22:59.772
mayn shvester hot zikh gelernt neyen

00:22:59.772 --> 00:23:00.841
in Sinever.

00:23:01.214 --> 00:23:03.206
deys hob ikh tsurikgenumen.

00:23:03.247 --> 00:23:03.705
THAT'S...

00:23:03.301 --> 00:23:04.315
mir redn

00:23:04.315 --> 00:23:05.923
vegn, shoyn nokhn

00:23:05.923 --> 00:23:06.772
krig.

00:23:06.348 --> 00:23:07.164
yo, nokhn krig.

00:23:07.695 --> 00:23:09.137
ven men hot aykh

00:23:10.170 --> 00:23:11.103
geheysn

00:23:11.103 --> 00:23:12.799
 geyn in geto,

00:23:12.799 --> 00:23:17.032
vi azoy zaynt ir gegangen? vi azoy zaynt ir gekumen in geto?

00:23:17.985 --> 00:23:22.045
di eltere mentshn zenen gezesn oyf di vegn.

00:23:22.334 --> 00:23:23.559
di kleyne kinder.

00:23:23.819 --> 00:23:31.145
undz ze'mir gegangen tsu fus, di dey k- gresere mentshn hot men nisht gelozt der hot nisht gelozt oyfzetsn zikh, der, der zogt er,

00:23:31.342 --> 00:23:35.677
"kenst geyn tsu fus." un ze'mir gegangen tsu fus, bay fus gegangen gantse shures.

00:23:36.662 --> 00:23:38.943
ze'mir gekumen oyf

00:23:39.020 --> 00:23:39.935
DRAHIV,

00:23:39.935 --> 00:23:42.398
dort hot men tsugeshtanen di andere,

00:23:42.398 --> 00:23:45.573
me hot genumen di yidn fun DRAHIV, vayl dort iz geven a sakh...

00:23:44.734 --> 00:23:45.853
vos iz DRAHIV?

00:23:45.825 --> 00:23:46.466
s'iz geven a,

00:23:46.529 --> 00:23:48.753
geven a dorf vu ze'mir durkhgegangen mit di deys,

00:23:48.823 --> 00:23:49.821
